---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
import me from '../../resources/result_ME.jpg';
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">

    <div class="name-block">
      <div class="avatar">
        <img src={me.src} alt="Moja fotka" class="avatar-image" />
      </div>

      <div class="name-text">
        <div class="name-row">
          <span class="n-bright">M</span><span class="n-ghost">arek</span>
        </div>
        <div class="name-row">
          <span class="n-bright">M</span><span class="n-ghost">azák</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-card">
      <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">3 +</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Roky testovania</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-sep"></div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">IT</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Enthusiast</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-sep"></div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">Bc.</span>
          <span class="stat-label">FRI Žilina</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="bio-block">
      <p class="bio-text">
        Som softvérový tester so zameraním na kvalitu a spoľahlivosť aplikácií.
        Popri testovaní ma zaujíma aj dátová analytika a práca s dátami.
        Rád sa učím nové technológie a získané poznatky využívam v praxi.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="info-block">
      <p class="info-label">Aktuálna pozícia</p>
      <p class="info-title">Automated Software Tester</p>
      <p class="info-sub">Scheidt &amp; Bachmann, Júl 2025 - súčasne</p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-block">
      <p class="info-label">Nástroje</p>
      <div class="chips">
        <span class="chip">Python</span>
        <span class="chip">SQL</span>
        <span class="chip">Java</span>
        <span class="chip">Robot Framework</span>
        <span class="chip">REST API</span>
        <span class="chip">SoapUI</span>
        <span class="chip">Bruno</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chips">
        <span class="chip">Git</span>
        <span class="chip">Linux (basic)</span>
        <span class="chip">UML</span>
        <span class="chip">Azure DevOps</span>
        <span class="chip">Jira</span>
        <span class="chip">Confluence</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chips">
        <span class="chip">AI asistenti</span>
        <span class="chip">R studio</span>  
        <span class="chip">Power BI</span>
        <span class="chip">Power Automate</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-block">
      <p class="info-label">Vzdelanie</p>

      <p class="info-title">Ing. Loading </p>
      <p class="info-sub">UNIZA FRI Žilina, 2024 - súčasne</p>
      <div class="progress-bar">
        <div class="progress-track">
          <div class="progress-fill"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="progress-label">90%</span>
      </div>

      <p class="info-title">Bc. Informatika a riadenie </p>
      <p class="info-thesis">Téma BP: Dátova analytika vo vzdelávaciom procese</p>
      <p class="info-sub">UNIZA FRI Žilina, 2021 - 2024</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="social-row">
      <a href="https://github.com/MazakMarek" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
